{"lastModified":1774282449689,"uri":"c::7579668770::vessel::d5ca718e-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Gulet","Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia, France, Greece, Naples, Marseille, Ionian Sea, Montenegro\n\nBuilt in 2017 by Turkish shipyard Big Blue Yachting, SATORI is a stunning sailing yacht with a distinctive dark blue hull, spacious decks and a shallow draft allowing for easy access to smaller ports, Her expansive outdoor areas offer multiple spots for unwinding and taking in the views, from serene lounging spaces to a sun deck complete with al fresco dining and an open-air cinema. For those who love the water, a swim platform with an extendable ladder provides easy access for swimming or enjoying the sea up close.\n\nInside, a chic and minimal design creates a calming, harmonious atmosphere. SATORI accommodates up to 10 guests in five luxurious cabins, including a full-beam master suite with a spacious en suite bathroom and private Hammam. One of the double guest cabins can be converted into a spa, treatment room, or gym, offering flexible options tailored to your charter experience.","blueprint":{"name":"SATORI","images":["/media/media::image::c::7579668770::vessel::d5ca718e-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::2a4b5110-26d3-11f1-9847-2b71f45ef063/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7579668770::vessel::d5ca718e-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::2a4b7820-26d3-11f1-9847-2b71f45ef063/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7579668770::vessel::d5ca718e-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::2a497c50-26d3-11f1-9847-2b71f45ef063/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7579668770::vessel::d5ca718e-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::2a50a840-26d3-11f1-9847-2b71f45ef063/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7579668770::vessel::d5ca718e-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::2a4dc210-26d3-11f1-9847-2b71f45ef063/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7579668770::vessel::d5ca718e-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::2a4584b0-26d3-11f1-